PAPIER-MACHE LETTER RACKS.

It’s a hand made Paper-Mache stationery product for office use and decor. Besides, its uses includes storing letters, doc holder and shelf decoration. These exquisite items have been hand painted by Kashmiri artists drawing inspiration from their beautiful legacy of art. This article contains a partition letter rack for different letter sizes.

Material:
    Mashed wood, Papier-Mache.
Care:
    Dust it with a soft cotton cloth to keep away the dirt.
Usage:
    Document holder, letter rack, Stationery stand, Home and Office decor.
Sizes:
    8’’ AND 10’’.
Shipping Info:
    Dispatched in a maximum of 6 business days
